### Economics: Token Economy and Cost Structures

| Coding Approach      | Upfront Cost (Capex) | Ongoing Cost (Opex)                  | Characteristics                                         |
|---------------------|---------------------|------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------|
| **Vibe Coding**      | Low                 | High                               | Minimal upfront effort; wastes tokens on trial/error; accumulates technical debt and maintenance costs. Often uses expensive models for simple tasks. |
| **Agentic Engineering** | High                | Low                                | Significant initial investment in building context, agents, sandboxes, and tests; dramatically reduces token consumption with efficient workflows; financially sustainable long-term. |

An important optimization is **intelligent model routing**, where the harness intelligently assigns tasks to the appropriate AI models based on complexity, reducing the premium use of large frontier models for trivial tasks.

